Tasks To Be Performed:
Create an instance in the US-East-1 (N. Virginia) region with Linux OS and manage the requirement of web servers of your company using AMI.
Replicate the instance in the US-West-2 (Oregon) region.
Build two EBS volumes and attach them to the instance in the US-East-1 (N. Virginia) region.
Delete one volume after detaching it and extend the size of the other volume.
Take backup of this EBS volume
